Game Info
Warcraft II Battle.net Edition is the continuation of the ruthless clash between
the armies of the noble humans and the brutish orcs. As the ruler of a medieval
empire, you must learn to carefully manage your limited resources while engaging
in real-time tactical warfare over land, sea, and air. This version of the classic
real-time strategy game combines the original Warcraft II: Tides of Darkness and
the Warcraft II: Beyond the Dark Portal expansion set with free Internet play over
Battle.net. Up to eight opponents from around the world can compete for dominance.

Install Notes
1. Mount/burn image
2. Install using one of the following serial numbers:
	H7BT-MDJX-MDTF-H9CM
	6696-2TGV-TT64-CNMV
	HTFW-F26Z-6P4W-N4PD
3. Update the game by installing War2Patch_202.exe from
	the Updates folder

*Note* The image must be mounted when playing

Release Info
Something different from me this time, but don't get used to it. After watching
the movie, I felt the urge to replay one of my favourite childhood games. After
failing to find a copy online, I found my own original CD and made an image for
the rest of you. Tested and working on Windows 7 and Windows 8, 64-bit
